metadata.name: Mfer Halloween Token
metadata.description:
The Mfer Halloween Token serves many purposes within the mfer community.

At mfer connect, we love to interview, interact, and collaborate within the mfer community, be it OGs or derivatives. We have just begun to really showcase the community through our collaborations, and there will be many more in the future.

Purchasing a token will help us to continue spreading the good word and vibe of mfers.

There will also be many other unique things we will be doing for the holders of these tokens. 

We will be revealing many more plans in the very near future. We feel like we will have some pleasant surprises in store to all holders of the tokens.

This is just the beginning mfers...
